    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>use the arguments <code>-Xms&lt;memory&gt;</code> <code>-Xmx&lt;memory&gt;</code>. Use <code>M</code> or <code>G</code> after the numbers for indicating Megs and Gigs of bytes respectively. <code>-Xms</code> indicates the minimum and <code>-Xmx</code> the maximum.</p>\n"
